&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is dedicated to keeping our candidate pipelines full, warm, and moving. The primary focus will be on&amp;nbsp;Advanced Practice Providers (APPs) and support for physician sourcing as needed. You will work closely with&amp;nbsp;our recruiters to ensure every handoff is clean, every outreach is strategic, and no great candidate goes cold. This&amp;nbsp;role reports directly to the Clinical Recruitment Manager, with a dotted-line reporting relationship to the Vice&amp;nbsp;President of Talent Acquisition for physician sourcing strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sourcing &amp;amp; Outreach&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Attracting CNMs, WHNPs, OB/GYNs, PAs, and other clinical providers across LinkedIn, Indeed,&amp;nbsp;ACNM/AANP chapters, Facebook groups, contact lists and niche clinical communities&lt;br&gt;• Run targeted outreach campaigns, track conversion rates, and maintain full, active pipelines across&amp;nbsp;all open markets&lt;br&gt;• Re-engage silver medalists and keep warm candidates from going cold between touchpoints&amp;nbsp;Screening &amp;amp; Candidate Handoff&lt;br&gt;• Conduct structured initial screens covering licensure, availability, location flexibility, and&amp;nbsp;compensation, providing a deeper touchpoint than a basic inquiry&lt;br&gt;• Deliver clean, polished candidate summaries to the assigned recruiter using a standardized screening&amp;nbsp;scorecard (in Greenhouse), so recruiters can focus on relationship-building in their screens&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Maintain consistent candidate communication between touchpoints until recruiter handoff&lt;br&gt;• Ensure all sourced candidates are tracked and up-to-date in the ATS at all times&lt;br&gt;• Provide daily pipeline updates on the recruiting tracker&amp;nbsp;Cross-Functional Support&lt;br&gt;• Support physician sourcing efforts as directed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Candidate Handoff Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sourced candidates will be assigned between recruiters on a rotating basis. You will work closely with&amp;nbsp;the recruitment manager and the clinical sourcer to maintain equal distribution.&lt;/p&gt;
